finish the rest.

513
00:22:26,833 --> 00:22:28,083
Makes sense.

514
00:22:28,166 --> 00:22:31,041
Yes, I agree. Sometimes
you just get hyper focused

515
00:22:31,125 --> 00:22:33,125
on something, like finding
the perfect Cartado,

516
00:22:33,208 --> 00:22:35,000
but it's more than
just a collectible!

517
00:22:35,083 --> 00:22:37,583
And the only way to truly
appreciate your new treasure

518
00:22:37,666 --> 00:22:39,375
is to make use of its power!

519
00:22:39,458 --> 00:22:42,333
Only then can one achieve
true Cartado nirvana!

520
00:22:42,416 --> 00:22:44,750
For that reason, I feel
like I failed my...

521
00:22:44,833 --> 00:22:46,458
It's totally blank.

522
00:22:46,541 --> 00:22:49,041
[RONA]
I do apologize, Yusha.

523
00:22:49,125 --> 00:22:51,416
Thanks, Rona. It's perfect!

524
00:22:51,500 --> 00:22:52,791
Huh?

525
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:57,458
[MAO] Okay. It's time to
take your seats, class.

526
00:22:57,541 --> 00:22:59,208
It's Miss Mao!

527
00:22:59,291 --> 00:23:00,250
[MAO]
What now?

528
00:23:00,333 --> 00:23:02,083
Our future is still
blank, right?

529
00:23:02,166 --> 00:23:03,500
So I was thinking,

530
00:23:03,583 --> 00:23:05,208
can we be whatever we want?

531
00:23:05,291 --> 00:23:08,625
Uh. Yeah, I don't see why not.

532
00:23:08,708 --> 00:23:11,125
[YUSHA]
Well, in that case,

533
00:23:11,208 --> 00:23:13,833
I'm going to be the Hero!

534
00:23:15,666 --> 00:23:17,416
Typical Yusha...

535
00:23:17,500 --> 00:23:18,958
That's a great idea.

536
00:23:19,041 --> 00:23:21,583
Duh, of course it is!
It's Yusha's!

537
00:23:21,666 --> 00:23:25,458
Okay! I'll pal with you!
'Cause that's just what pals do!

538
00:23:25,541 --> 00:23:27,833
Great job! You are amazing!

539
00:23:27,916 --> 00:23:28,791
--[CHIBI sighs]
--[GIRLS gasp]

540
00:23:28,875 --> 00:23:30,750
[chirps]

541
00:23:30,833 --> 00:23:32,083
[YUSHA]
Aw, Chibi!

542
00:23:32,166 --> 00:23:33,666
[SEIRA]
When did you get here?

543
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:34,625
[FAI]
Maybe she can teleport!

544
00:23:34,708 --> 00:23:38,375
Oh my goodness. [sighs]

545
00:23:38,458 --> 00:23:41,875
The problem with Heroes is they
never know when to give up.

546
00:23:41,958 --> 00:23:45,875
Well, you'd better give
it your best, Yusha!

547
00:23:45,958 --> 00:23:47,875
Right! I promise.

548
00:23:47,958 --> 00:23:49,708
I won't fail!

